<doc id="1237436" wikidata="Q172053" url="?curid=1237436" title="Luiz Bueno">
<text>Luiz-Pereira Bueno also known as Luiz Bueno (16 January 1937 – 8 February 2011) was a race car driver from Brazil. He participated in one World Championship Formula One Grand Prix, on 11 February 1973. He scored no championship points. He also participated in several non-championship Formula One races.

Bueno died of cancer, aged 74.
